These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, folk
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | baccarat |
| Music-Genre     | folk | electronic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, chaman
2 different pets are kept: turtle, pony
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Cigar    | dunhill      | chaman         |
| Pet   | turtle | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, journalist
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, french
1. the paramedic is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Job   | journalist | paramedic   |
| Nationality       | french  | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, peach
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Food   | nectarine  | peach |
| Flower         | poppy | azalea    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, cycling
